      "body" : "There's no telling what compilers will do to this. If you're that concerned about timing attacks, why not just do something like this pseudocode?\r\n```\r\nconst minwait = 50; //msec\r\ntimeBefore = GetCurrentTime();\r\nresult = val1 == val2;\r\nsleep(minwait - (GetCurrentTime() - timeBefore));\r\nreturn result;\r\n```",
